tables.images:
CREATE TABLE `images` (
  `ImageID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `ImageURL` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Description` text,
  `Is_Public` tinyint DEFAULT NULL,
  `Name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`ImageID`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4061 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.image_tags:
CREATE TABLE `image_tags` (
  `ImageID` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `TagID` int DEFAULT NULL,
  KEY `fk_image_id` (`ImageID`),
  KEY `fk_tag_id` (`TagID`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_image_id` FOREIGN KEY (`ImageID`) REFERENCES `images` (`ImageID`) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `fk_tag_id` FOREIGN KEY (`TagID`) REFERENCES `tags` (`TagID`) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `image_tags_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`ImageID`) REFERENCES `images` (`ImageID`),
  CONSTRAINT `image_tags_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`TagID`) REFERENCES `tags` (`TagID`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.role_permissions:
CREATE TABLE `role_permissions` (
  `id` int NOT NULL,
  `role_id` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `permission_level` int DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `role_id` (`role_id`),
  CONSTRAINT `role_permissions_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`role_id`) REFERENCES `roles` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.roles:
CREATE TABLE `roles` (
  `id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `name` (`name`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.sticker_templates:
CREATE TABLE `sticker_templates` (
  `id` bigint unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `design_data` json DEFAULT NULL,
  `image_id` int DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.tags:
CREATE TABLE `tags` (
  `TagID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `TagName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`TagID`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=31 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.user_favorites:
CREATE TABLE `user_favorites` (
  `user_id` int NOT NULL,
  `image_id` int NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`user_id`,`image_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.user_roles:
CREATE TABLE `user_roles` (
  `user_id` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `role_id` int NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`user_id`,`role_id`),
  KEY `role_id` (`role_id`),
  CONSTRAINT `user_roles_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`user_id`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `user_roles_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`role_id`) REFERENCES `roles` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.user_sessions:
CREATE TABLE `user_sessions` (
  `userid` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cookie` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expire` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  UNIQUE KEY `userid` (`userid`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
tables.users:
CREATE TABLE `users` (
  `id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `display_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `profPic` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `provider` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `password` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  UNIQUE KEY `unique_email_provider` (`email`,`provider`),
  KEY `idx_user_id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
